00:14:45,779 --> 00:14:48,863
then they're not going to be activities that the player engages in.

262
00:14:48,863 --> 00:14:53,027
And so one thing that I always recommend when we're talking to developers

263
00:14:53,027 --> 00:14:54,689
is when you're thinking about these systems,

264
00:14:54,689 --> 00:14:55,870
when you're thinking about content,

265
00:14:55,870 --> 00:14:57,812
when you're thinking about all these necessary ways

266
00:14:57,812 --> 00:15:00,676
to layer in this activity into a game,

267
00:15:00,676 --> 00:15:02,518
to include this on your checklist.

268
00:15:02,518 --> 00:15:06,542
You know, how are you building volition in engaging in the activity?

