00:15:59,532 --> 00:16:04,035
So there's opportunities to satisfy relatedness, there's opportunities.

287
00:16:04,035 --> 00:16:07,558
It's creating those structures that telegraph or communicate

288
00:16:07,558 --> 00:16:11,140
need satisfaction that actually build that volitional engagement

289
00:16:11,140 --> 00:16:16,004
and not just giving them a lot of freedom to do whatever they want to do.

290
00:16:16,004 --> 00:16:17,585
Even if the game is enormous.

291
00:16:19,085 --> 00:16:21,087
and it's filled with tons of activities,

292
00:16:21,087 --> 00:16:24,970
it doesn't matter if the player doesn't see meaning

